Package: {{PACKAGE_NAME}}
Version: {{VERSION}}
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: OpenAssetWatch <noreply@openassetwatch.example>
Depends: systemd, passwd
Installed-Size: 1
Description: OpenAssetWatch defensive local asset inventory agent
 The OpenAssetWatch agent collects local, passive asset inventory
 observations for administrator-approved OpenAssetWatch deployments.
 This package installs a conservative one-shot systemd service and timer
 for the production Linux agent runtime.
